Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.73,0:00:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.76,0:00:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger,\Nthe King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.66,0:00:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.97,0:00:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before\Nhis death drove people to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.84,0:00:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?\NIf you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.67,0:00:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.85,0:00:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men head for the\NGrand Line in pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly\Nentered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.49,0:00:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.86,0:00:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.97,0:00:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever,\NI take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.35,0:01:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.17,0:01:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard\Nsomeone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.65,0:01:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.94,0:01:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Worst Man in the Eastern Seas!\NFishman Pirate Arlong!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.44,0:02:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The weather's so great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.68,0:02:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the Grand Line far,\Nfar away that way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or is it maybe this way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.42,0:02:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way?! This way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.13,0:02:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're annoying. Sit still, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.76,0:02:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.57,0:02:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we finally have a cook,\Nso now we just need to get Nami back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:03:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then we're finally\Ngoing into the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.01,0:03:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.77,0:03:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just remembering her beautiful\Nvisage makes me happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.51,0:03:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How I can't wait to see her again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.85,0:03:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yosaku. We're almost\Nto where Nami is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys're soft-minded!\NToo soft-minded! Don't you get it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.83,0:03:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minute by minute, we're heading\Nright for the infamous Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.23,0:03:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis's eyes were glued to\NArlong's picture when she saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.54,0:03:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wasn't her normal self!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis Nami plans to take down Arlong
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.15,0:03:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and collect his\N20 million-Berry bounty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She may already be inside\Nhis compound as we speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Well, let's have some food!\N--Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.36,0:04:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.50,0:04:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you guys've\Nnever heard of Arlong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong? Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.57,0:04:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never heard of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, listen up! I guess I'll just\Nhave to fill you in about everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong is a fishman who used to\Nrampage throughout the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fishman?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fishman, huh? I haven't met one yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.79,0:04:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, I hear the mermaids on\NFishman Island in the Grand Line
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.73,0:04:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are absolutely beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.86,0:04:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are fishmen...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.13,0:04:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's a masterpiece!\N--Can't you guys stay focused?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, then. I'll explain\Nfrom the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason the Grand Line's called\Na pirate graveyard in the first place
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is because of the three\Npowers that reign over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.15,0:04:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of which is the\NSeven Warlords of the Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.89,0:05:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven Warlords?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Simply put, they're\Ngovernment-authorized pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.16,0:05:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why would pirates\Nget a government's approval?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.93,0:05:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By paying the government a cut\Nof the loot they take from pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Seven Warlords\Nare allowed to exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.91,0:05:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other pirates' eyes, they're\Nno more than "government dogs,"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.85,0:05:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they're strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.19,0:05:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Hawk-Eye Mihawk, the guy\NBig Bro Zoro lost to, is a Warlord!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.96,0:05:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's awesome!\NThere's seven of those guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Seven Warlords are awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, one of the Seven Warlords\Nis Jimbei, a fishman pirate boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the fishman Arlong is\Na pirate right on par with him
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who used to commit atrocity\Nafter atrocity in the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:05:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.28,0:06:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just your last picture standing up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.69,0:06:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong has rule over 20 towns\Nsince coming to the East Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.23,0:06:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His strength is\Nfar superior to Don Krieg's!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why would Nami-san\Ngo to this guy all by herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.53,0:06:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, she's after\Nthe bounty on his head!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.64,0:06:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, who knows? Maybe Nami-san\Nis actually a mermaid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially given how lovely she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.71,0:06:30.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Nami"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.71,0:06:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you guys even understand\Nwhat I've told you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.29,0:06:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, there's a strong\Nfishman, right? We get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.89,0:06:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you don't get it! You don't\Nknow how strong fishmen are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.93,0:06:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll find out when we\Nget there. Quit worrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.83,0:06:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, let's have some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.67,0:06:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.94,0:06:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Food?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.64,0:06:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.07,0:06:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat things with bones in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.28,0:06:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want sautéed bean sprouts!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.01,0:07:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.55,0:07:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be done in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.35,0:07:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat and bean sprouts...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Having a cook really is great!\N--Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.89,0:07:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat! A jumbo serving of meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.56,0:07:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And bean sprouts for me!\NA jumbo serving!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back here again...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.15,0:07:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My... hometown...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.77,0:07:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Here is this\Nmonth's amount. Accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.01,0:08:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're on a completely different level\Nof intellect than ordinary pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.18,0:08:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You truly know how\Nto get ahead in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.18,0:08:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Likewise!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.62,0:08:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Befriending me means you can\Nmilk the East Blue all you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a navy colonel,\Nyou're wise to realize that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.23,0:08:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A good world is one in\Nwhich money flows well!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.63,0:08:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Money is good. You can\Ntrust it more than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.27,0:08:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.71,0:08:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.21,0:08:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate humans, but good sports\Nlike you are an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I should be going...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come drink with us sometime!\NLet's have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not good for a navy ship on patrol\Nto be stopped at a pirate island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill anyone for you\Nwho tells headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:09:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll be leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.30,0:09:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! The colonel's heading back!\NTake him to his ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.54,0:09:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.67,0:09:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get in the octopus pot!\NI'll take you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.68,0:09:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you always have such a funny face!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.35,0:09:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks just like a rat's!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hachi! Watch your mouth!\NThe colonel is a valued guest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.52,0:09:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.93,0:09:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn fishmen. You're creepy as hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're great as pay dirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to kill Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong killed my daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move, or I'll kill you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong doesn't have time to\Nbother with little brats like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.01,0:10:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.82,0:10:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use that to at least keep yourself safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You're back, Nami!\NThat was a long trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? How was your haul this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.74,0:10:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't have gone better!\NI earned a ton!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.81,0:10:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found so many suckers who are\Nfooled so easily! As you can see!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Betrayal is your forte!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.15,0:10:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:11:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Brothers! Our friend\Nhas returned! Prepare a party!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.52,0:11:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's Nami!\N--Nami's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.63,0:11:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-We're finally here! Arlong Park!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.37,0:11:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the hideout\Nof the fishman Arlong,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who came from the Grand Line?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.81,0:12:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Nami really here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.48,0:12:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis Nami was on the Going Merry,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.05,0:12:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so let's first see if it's\Nstopped on this island or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.72,0:12:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.43,0:12:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're busting in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.06,0:12:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why are we suddenly doing that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.43,0:12:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?!\NWe haven't even found any clues yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.27,0:12:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're dealing with\Nthose fishmen, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.67,0:12:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta have a strategy first!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.61,0:12:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget that tedious stuff.\NLuffy told me to bring her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.75,0:12:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna do just that,\Nno matter who we're dealing with!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.69,0:12:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.15,0:12:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is! I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Going Merry! It's over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.23,0:12:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Big Sis Nami is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.60,0:13:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!\NWhat's the big idea?! Untie me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.44,0:13:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're farther east of Arlong Park...\NCocoyashi Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.58,0:13:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's strange. Why's the ship\Nstopped so far from the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.28,0:13:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Untie me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.62,0:13:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been hurt so bad\Nyou're nearly dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just take it easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.96,0:13:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave this all to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am so going to chop him up someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring the girl back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.17,0:13:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in high spirits, now that\Nyou know she's not in Arlong Park...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.74,0:13:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right rudder, full!\NPull the boat up to the Going Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.35,0:13:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I hereby title\Nthis brave image of me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.75,0:13:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about to tread unknown soil,\N"Captain Usopp's Grand Adventure"!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There! There!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.27,0:14:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fishmen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.51,0:14:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Full speed ahead!\N--Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you just pass by it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.52,0:14:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see that?!\NThere were fishmen there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.48,0:14:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're Arlong's crew! They're scary!\NSomethin' wrong with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you snap at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.72,0:14:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this whole area is\Nseriously under Arlong's control!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.19,0:14:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! We'll just say we\Ncouldn't bring Nami back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.93,0:14:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Untie me, you idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.20,0:14:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Never seen that boat before.\N--It's suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Escape!\N--Agreed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.32,0:14:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! At least untie me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.99,0:15:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's just him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.69,0:15:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you banished from\Nsomewhere or somethin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.90,0:15:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.57,0:15:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kill those guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.60,0:15:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! So you got these injuries\Nfrom being tortured!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.40,0:15:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's take him\Nback to Arlong-san for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive us, Zoro! I'll tell Luffy\Nyou were a truly brave man!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.51,0:15:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an unlucky person!\NI'll never forget about you, Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.68,0:15:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then!\NLet's get on dry land for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.79,0:15:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There should be a town\Ncalled Gosa up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.11,0:15:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What happened to this town?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.65,0:16:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard Arlong ravaged it\Na few weeks back, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-All the houses have been flipped over!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.49,0:16:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear fishmen generally have\Nten times the strength of humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.30,0:16:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In short, could this be how strong\Npeople from the Grand Line are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.61,0:16:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how'd even the street get like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the doing\Nof a monster called Momoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.45,0:16:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place even has monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.85,0:16:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We brought him from the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.59,0:16:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the Grand Line, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.89,0:16:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"We"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're with that guy who\Ngot banished, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.87,0:16:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.30,0:16:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.30,0:16:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Escaped by a hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stay safe, Big Bro Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.11,0:17:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to wait here for\NYosaku and Big Bro Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.78,0:17:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if a fishman can possibly\Ncatch me on dry land!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.55,0:17:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to this!\NJust try and catch up to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.83,0:17:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found you, fishman!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You killed my daddy!\NAnd I'm gonna kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with the fishmen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.37,0:17:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.47,0:17:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone here in Gosa
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.54,0:17:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was slaughtered because just\None villager defied them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.85,0:17:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You look like a fishman,\Nbut you're human. Just barely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.08,0:17:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just barely?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.09,0:17:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?! Over there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.52,0:17:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fishman!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.19,0:17:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a real one, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.10,0:17:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back! I, Captain Usopp,\Nwill protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.00,0:17:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can handle one easily enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.87,0:18:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! Special Attack: Lead Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.58,0:18:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one ever listens!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, the fishmen'll\Nkill us if we mess with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.56,0:18:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What is it?!\N--There was a long-nosed man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.26,0:18:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Where'd he go?!\N--That way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.23,0:18:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! We'll carry him to my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.98,0:18:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That looks great!\N--Lemme see, lemme see!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.49,0:19:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess that's good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.89,0:19:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momoo! Time to eat! Momoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.53,0:19:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange.\NHe should be starving by now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.97,0:19:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where could he have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.85,0:19:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're great, Big Bro Sanji!\NThis is topnotch seasoning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.62,0:19:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make dinner for Nami-san\Nmore than I do for you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.06,0:20:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you manage to get\NBig Sis Nami to join again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will! She's our navigator!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's going to the Grand Line with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.54,0:20:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's mine!\N--You just ate one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.07,0:20:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me have one, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--But it's mine!\N--C'mon, just one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.31,0:20:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No! Give it back!\N--C'mon! Let me have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.38,0:20:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit rockin' the damn boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to make me\Nspill this fine alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.69,0:20:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.23,0:20:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've brought someone suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.97,0:20:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask again.\NJust why have you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.78,0:21:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you already-- I'm looking\Nfor a girl! Half-fish bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.39,0:21:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a big mouth\Nfor a lowly human.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.39,0:21:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll excuse you this time,\Nbut never say "half-fish" again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.86,0:21:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We fishmen are "evolved humans"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.99,0:21:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who've gained the ability\Nto breathe underwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.10,0:21:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those fish abilities result\Nin us being superior to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.87,0:21:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As proof, we possess numerous\Nabilities that surpass those of humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get it through your head that\Nfishmen are the lord of all things!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.35,0:21:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans defying fishmen is basically\Ndefying the laws of nature!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of those ridiculous\Nopinions of yours, Arlong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.42,0:21:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look so stern, Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may be human,\Nbut you're an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.50,0:21:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a skilled surveyor and prized\Nmember of the Arlong Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.20,0:21:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You make truly accurate\Nsea charts for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.30,0:21:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have far more smarts than\Nyou guys. It's only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.14,0:21:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Nami! What does\Nhe mean, "surveyor"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.01,0:22:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you acting all\Nfriendly-like with this guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.05,0:22:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? He's an acquaintance of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.75,0:22:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous.\NHe was just my prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.85,0:22:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swiped a whole load of treasure\Nfrom this guy this time around.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.29,0:22:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think he'd follow me here,\Nwithout any idea he'd been tricked...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.26,0:22:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about unbelievably stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.43,0:22:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So these are your true colors, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.83,0:22:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After you hated pirates so much before.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.43,0:22:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surprised? It was all an act.\NDoes this make it clear enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.87,0:22:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.78,0:22:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a pirate, plain and simple!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.29,0:22:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a leader of the Arlong Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.07,0:23:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My overflowing feelings don't connect
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.07,0:23:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as I firmly squeeze your hand back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.98,0:23:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll set off by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.91,0:23:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so keep watching me intently\Nas I go into the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.76,0:23:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about it\Na bit since this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.76,0:23:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it so hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.33,0:23:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting from some point, I haven't\Nbeen able to get away from that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.81,0:23:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to catch those\Nfeelings that rushed off,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.68,0:23:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm already about\Nto overtake myself, even
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.56,0:23:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to embrace my\Ndreams that have jumped out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.56,0:24:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you, I can run there
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.21,0:24:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently Arlong and the\Nfishmen rule this village,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.64,0:24:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and no one can oppose them!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.75,0:24:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Don't tell me\Nfish cuisine isn't allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.25,0:24:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I prefer meat with a bone in it!\NSanji! More meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.19,0:24:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think she'd team up\Nwith the fishmen...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.32,0:24:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't Nami one of us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.92,0:24:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.33,0:24:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Witch of Cocoyashi Village!\NArlong's Female Leader"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.53,0:24:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.30,0:24:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
